FBIS4-59797 "drnes096_l_94001" FBIS-NES-94-096 Daily Report 17 May 1994 ISRAEL Peres Terms 'Arafat Remarks `Unfounded,' `Amazing' Peres Terms 'Arafat Remarks `Unfounded,' `Amazing' TA1705143994 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1400 GMT 17 May 94 TA1705143994 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Hebrew BFN [Text] Foreign Minister Shim'on Peres has termed unfounded the remarks 'Arafat made about a letter he had received from the Israeli Government regarding the future of Jerusalem. Minister Peres also said that 'Arafat's statement about the need to continue jihad is amazing and totally unacceptable. Israel will examine what exactly 'Arafat said and will respond in kind. Minister Peres made these remarks to our correspondent Shlomo Raz.
